<p>Subsecs. (b)(2)(B), (c)(1). <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._101-549">Pub. L. 101–549, § 212(b)</a>, (c), inserted reference to<a aria-label="Definitions -  nonroad engine " class="colorbox-load definedterm" href="/definitions/uscode.php?width=840&amp;height=800&amp;iframe=true&amp;def_id=42-USC-291775061-1836750022&amp;term_occur=999&amp;term_src="> nonroad engine </a>or<a aria-label="Definitions -  nonroad vehicle." class="colorbox-load definedterm" href="/definitions/uscode.php?width=840&amp;height=800&amp;iframe=true&amp;def_id=42-USC-1893963399-1836750023&amp;term_occur=999&amp;term_src="> nonroad vehicle.</a></p>
